@page "/education"
@using MudBlazor
<PageTitle>Baivel - Education</PageTitle>

<div style="width:100%;height:100%" id="fond">
	<div style="height:100%;margin-top:-64px;" id="home-background">
		<div style="background-color: #717486bf;">
			<MudItem Style="padding-top:100px;height:max-content;padding-bottom: 36px;">
				<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" Style="font-family:'Cascadia Code'" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Center">Education</MudText>
			</MudItem>
			<div style="background-color:white;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;border-radius:15px;padding:10px" id="cadre">
				<MudStack Row="true" Wrap="Wrap.Wrap" Style="width:100%;margin-top:20px;height: 50vh;" Spacing="5" Justify="Justify.SpaceEvenly">
					<MudItem Style="width:40%;align-content: center;" id="aboutme">
						<MudItem Class="pb-5">
							<MudText Typo="Typo.h4" Color="Color.Primary">Master Degree In Computer Science</MudText>
							<MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Color="Color.Primary">2021-2026</MudText>
							</MudItem>
						<MudText Align="Align.Justify" Color="Color.Primary">
							I'v been studying for 3 years and a half at the french engineering school, CY Tech, to get a engineering degree, the equivalent of a master degree. 
							In this school, I've studied C, SQL, Java even a little bit of Python. 
							I also learned the basics of Linux, of network architecture and of code testing. <br />
							During my classes, I did a few projects that you can find here :
						</MudText>
						<MudButton Color="Color.Secondary" Variant="Variant.Filled" Style="font-size:15px;margin-top:15px" Href="/projects">My projects</MudButton>
					</MudItem>
					<MudItem Style="width:40%;align-content: center;">
						<MudImage Fluid="true" Src="images/campuscytechcergy.jpg" />
					</MudItem>
				</MudStack>

				<MudStack Row="true" Wrap="Wrap.Wrap" Style="width:100%;margin-top:20px;min-height: 50vh;" Spacing="5" Justify="Justify.SpaceEvenly">
					<MudItem Style="width:40%;padding-right:50px;align-content: center;">
						<MudImage Fluid="true" Src="images/pexels-divinetechygirl-1181675.jpg" />
					</MudItem>
					<MudItem Style="width:40%;align-content: center;" id="aboutme">
						<MudText Align="Align.Justify" Color="Color.Primary">
							In the context of my study, I am in a program where I alternate between weeks of school and weeks of work. I've been in this program for a year and a half. 
							<br />
							I'm working as a software developer half of the time and you can find details about my work here :
						</MudText>
						<MudButton Color="Color.Secondary" Variant="Variant.Filled" Style="font-size:15px;margin-top:15px" Href="/work">My work</MudButton>
					</MudItem>
				</MudStack>
			</div>
			<br />
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
